    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a functional choice for someone looking for a reliable daily driver at a lower price point. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows noticeable cosmetic wear, including some scratches on the exterior and visible aging in the upholstery. It has been maintained regularly, but a few minor mechanical components, such as the suspension and brake pads, will likely need attention in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done but could use some TLC to bring it back to its best.",
