    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical excellence and refined styling. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure peak performance and long-term reliability. The exterior maintains a sophisticated presence, while the interior offers a clean, well-preserved environment for the discerning driver. This vehicle represents a premier choice for those seeking a balance of prestige and proven durability. Available now for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really wonderful shape! It runs smoothly and has been well-loved, making it perfect for your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. I\u2019ve truly enjoyed driving it, and I think you will too! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus. This driver\u2019s spec includes a 6-speed Getrag manual transaxle and has been proactively serviced with an IMS bearing retrofit and a newer water pump for cooling system integrity. The suspension geometry is well-preserved, utilizing Bilstein B6 dampers that complement the factory multi-link rear setup. The braking system features four-piston monobloc calipers with plenty of bite remaining on the cross-drilled rotors. While the exterior shows honest road patina, the powertrain remains tight with no bore scoring symptoms and a clean oil analysis. A technically sound entry into 911 ownership for the performance-minded purist.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Reliable engine. Clean interior. Minor exterior wear. Maintenance up to date.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of pride in ownership, offering a reliable and comfortable driving experience. The exterior finish maintains a high-gloss luster, though close inspection reveals minor, age-appropriate stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper. Inside, the interior is impressively preserved; the upholstery is free of tears or odors, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control and premium audio system\u2014functioning perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a consistent maintenance log. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes provide firm, responsive stopping power. With a fresh oil change and tires at 70% tread, this car is fully prepared for its next chapter.",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
